			<h4><a id="comment_link_64121425" name="comment_link_64121425" href="//slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23178163&amp;cid=64121425" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64121425)" >It's just dot.com all over again</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64121425" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64121425); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>3</a>)</span></h4>
